CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A11, reads: "Meet the Springers - On the Job - Cecile Springer appears busy with the test tubes in laboratory of the University of Pittsburgh's Graduate School of Public Health. She is a bio-chemist there. - All Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Cecile Springer operating equipment in organic chemistry laboratory, at University of Pittsburgh
